	   <tr><td colspan=2>My piercing is going up so slowly it's killing me.&nbsp;&nbsp;I have a bloodstained fang.  Should I get a less damaging weapon but much faster delay to get my skill up faster?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
