	   <tr><td colspan=2>Give up your piercing self and embrace the power of the two hand blunt!<br>Sure a piercer is fine if you are going to med with the girly man.&nbsp;&nbsp;But if you want to melee with the boys you'll need a real weapon....e/g  <br><br>To learn any new weapon skill you should get your skill near 20 by training.  Once you get your skill above 20 you should notice it going up faster.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
